    participant U as Pengguna
    participant B as Halaman Profil
    participant C as ProfileController
    participant E as Entity User/Progress/QuizScore

    U->>B: Klik icon profil
    B->>U: Tampilkan dropdown menu
    U->>B: Pilih menu "Profile"
    B->>C: GET /profile
    
    C->>E: getUserData()
    E-->>C: data user (nama, email)
    
    C->>E: getProgressCount()
    E-->>C: jumlah materi selesai
    
    C->>E: getTotalMaterials()
    E-->>C: total materi
    
    C->>E: getQuizScores()
    E-->>C: riwayat nilai quiz
    
    C->>C: hitungRataRata()
    
    C-->>B: Kirim data lengkap
    B-->>U: Tampilkan profil + progres + riwayat nilai
